{
  "stem": "9777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were smuggling out some of the supplies-- injection needles and syringes and towels and sheets and whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wrapped it around ourselves and then the girls stuck in the needles in between the sheets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got undressed about a block away by a-- a Jewish seamstress, which I never knew they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents survived in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father came back from forced labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was over the age what the Germans were more or less interested to use like forced labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they survived in that new Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lived by my uncle, the one which one lives still in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was away in forced labor, and my aunt and her mother and her sister had lived in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they took us in for, like, boarders.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They vacated for us one room, and then another couple came whose-- the menfolks were away, so the three of us, we were in one room.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then another couple from across the street with two children moved into another room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's how they [INAUDIBLE] actually accumulated the Jewish people under the same roof.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More, the merrier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the days we spent in the air raid shelter in the basement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had very little freedom of going out or earn a living or anything of that sort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What the ghetto closed, was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not when I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't go to work account of I worked, like, in the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the air raid usually started around 9:00-- 8:30, 9:00, so--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, so before you started out, you had to end up in the basement. 5:00 was closing time, should we say.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
